The Telegraph - Calcutta (Kolkata) | Sports | ICC awards 
                                                                                                                       7                                      ICC awards 
            A STAFF REPORTER                      
	Calcutta: The ICC on Tuesday, announced that the 7th LG ICC awards ceremony will be held in Bangalore on October 6.         
	In this edition, the ICC awards ceremony will feature a new category, the Peoples Choice award. Fans across the globe will get a chance to vote for their favourite player on-line from a short-list of five cricketers, who will be selected by the ICC selection panel.                                                                                                                     
